1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 18=

4
00:00:23,359 --> 00:00:24,600
Miss, bad news!

5
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:26,039
Peng Dasheng went to the Heroes' Arena.

6
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,280
What for?

7
00:00:27,559 --> 00:00:28,879
I heard he went to accuse Mr. Song

8
00:00:28,879 --> 00:00:30,199
of colluding with the Demon Sect.

9
00:00:30,359 --> 00:00:31,640
But he has no solid proof.

10
00:00:31,839 --> 00:00:33,679
Now they're making him take
three strikes from Mr. Song

11
00:00:33,799 --> 00:00:35,679
to prove he's telling the truth.

12
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:39,560
Song Qingbo's Mountain-Splitting Palm
is vicious and deadly.

13
00:00:39,799 --> 00:00:40,320
Three strikes

14
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:41,600
could kill him.

15
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:43,320
Ready the horses.
We're going to the Heroes' Arena.

16
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,079
But, Miss,

17
00:00:44,079 --> 00:00:45,640
Master ordered you
not to leave the manor today.

18
00:00:45,679 --> 00:00:47,119
I'll explain it to Father.

19
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
(I'll put everything I have
into these three strikes.)

20
00:00:55,359 --> 00:00:57,679
(That brat won't leave here alive.)

21
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:02,840
Peng Dasheng,

22
00:01:03,399 --> 00:01:05,799
it's not too late to back out.

23
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:09,000
Once we start, I won't hold back,

24
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:12,079
even if it leaves you dead
or badly hurt.

25
00:01:14,319 --> 00:01:16,359
Mr. Song,
you're not going soft, are you?

26
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,959
Or did you bluff your way

27
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:21,920
into becoming sect leader?

28
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:25,920
You fool. Prepare to die!

29
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:42,200
Master, the Yizihuijian Sect's
Mountain-Splitting Palm

30
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,599
is known for its brute force.

31
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,000
Song Qingbo has honed

32
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,879
the technique to perfection.

33
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:49,879
But he doesn't know

34
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,760
your spiritual power is protecting you.

35
00:01:54,079 --> 00:01:57,599
Master, shield your Danzhong acupoint
with spiritual power.

36
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,799
Even his strongest strike

37
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:00,480
can't match a tenth

38
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:03,079
of your spiritual power.

39
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:06,040
Despite his age,

40
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,560
Mr. Peng took that strike

41
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,080
with pure inner force.

42
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:11,560
What a rare talent!

43
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:15,400
Are you all right?

44
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:21,120
Mr. Song, was that supposed to tickle?

45
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:23,919
Or haven't you eaten today?

46
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:27,159
Boy, you relied on your inner force

47
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:28,599
to withstand my Mountain-Splitting Palm.

48
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:29,479
That doesn't count!

49
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,199
The rules only say he can't fight back.

50
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,560
They never said
he couldn't use inner force.

51
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:35,280
Mr. Song, if you're not good enough,
go train some more.

52
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,800
Stop twisting the rules

53
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,560
and making a fool of yourself.

54
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:38,159
You...

55
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,400
Ms. Duan,

56
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:41,680
don't worry.

57
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,280
Song Qingbo,

58
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,240
if it bothers you that much,

59
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,199
then I'll take

60
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,120
your second strike without using

61
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,639
any inner force.

62
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:54,439
How's that?

63
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:01,680
You said it yourself.

64
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,800
What kind of technique is that?

65
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,599
Why is it so strange?

66
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:15,319
What...?

67
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:21,280
Song Qingbo, your nails are pitch-black.

68
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,680
Looks like a nasty infection.

69
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:25,680
You should see a doctor.

70
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:27,439
Mr. Qiu, look.

71
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,680
That wasn't a palm technique.

72
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,080
It was a claw technique.

73
00:03:30,319 --> 00:03:33,280
When Mr. Song gathered his qi,

74
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:35,479
his fingers curled like steel hooks.

75
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:39,520
He turned his palm force
into a claw strike.

76
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,639
That vicious technique

77
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:43,879
can't belong to an orthodox school.

78
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:45,479
That's right.

79
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:47,680
It's a forbidden art
of the Yizihuijian Sect.

80
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:49,800
His palm is laced with a rare poison
from the Western Regions.

81
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,639
One hit will sever the heart meridians
and kill its victim.

82
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,680
Master,

83
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:56,479
I don't know
how you'll survive this one.

84
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,199
My master always says,

85
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,080
hard force is like a raging flood,

86
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,280
while soft force flows like water.

87
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,560
No matter how fierce the flood,

88
00:04:02,599 --> 00:04:04,080
a winding stream can still

89
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,280
turn it aside.

90
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,560
Hmph! Let's see

91
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:11,240
whether you'll still be smiling
after this.

92
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,400
This strike

93
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:17,160
will tear your heart meridians apart.

94
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:30,240
Peng Dasheng, die!

95
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,079
Oh, no.

96
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:33,360
Song Qingbo is too cunning

97
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,360
to fall for that.

98
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,560
Cunning men like him
are always overconfident.

99
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,279
One false opening,

100
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:42,079
and he'll take the bait.

101
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:07,560
Impossible!
You stopped using your inner force.

102
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,279
How could you...?

103
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,079
Martial arts aren't only

104
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:10,839
about brute force.

105
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,600
You're a sect leader.

106
00:05:12,759 --> 00:05:14,279
Don't tell me you don't even know that.

107
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:17,879
Mr. Peng waited for the strike,
then slipped behind Mr. Song.

108
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,879
It looked effortless,

109
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,680
but every move flowed

110
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:24,480
with the force of Mr. Song's palm.

111
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:28,639
He has truly grasped
the essence of martial arts.

112
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:31,399
Mr. Peng already has

113
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:33,240
such insight and skill at his age.

114
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,800
There's no telling how far

115
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:37,079
he'll go in martial arts.

116
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,199
You brat!

117
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,800
You played dirty!

118
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:43,240
You played dirty first!

119
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,160
That claw strike was vicious.

120
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,879
You were trying to kill me.

121
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:48,480
Standing still and taking it

122
00:05:48,839 --> 00:05:49,959
would've been idiotic.

123
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:50,279
You...

124
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,040
Song Qingbo, at your age,

125
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,639
you're still playing dirty?

126
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,680
Have you no shame?

127
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:57,879
Amitabha.

128
00:05:57,959 --> 00:06:01,560
Mr. Song, I saw everything clearly.

129
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:05,040
You broke the rules first.

130
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,920
Mr. Song,

131
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:11,399
you only have one strike left, right?

132
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,199
Shut up!

133
00:06:13,079 --> 00:06:15,279
Outrageous!

134
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,399
How did Song Qingbo's inner force

135
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:24,040
become so powerful?

136
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:26,839
Mr. Song is using genuine qi

137
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:28,399
to draw the Heart-Eroding Miasma
out of his body.

138
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:31,879
The black mist around his palm
is years of accumulated baleful energy.

139
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:33,720
A single touch will sever the meridians.

140
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,439
Even someone with an invulnerable body

141
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:37,199
couldn't withstand it.

142
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,439
I never expected

143
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,279
Mr. Song's cultivation

144
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:43,639
to advance this much in just one year.

145
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:47,639
Mr. Peng may not survive this.

146
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,319
Peng Dasheng, die!

147
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,680
Ms. Murong!

148
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:26,680
What?

149
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,079
Bingqing!

150
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:35,959
Bingqing!

151
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,120
Bingqing!

152
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:43,040
Are you all right, Bingqing?

153
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,639
Father...

154
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,839
Protect Dasheng.

155
00:07:53,199 --> 00:07:54,079
Someone!

156
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,000
Take her home

157
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,279
and have her treated.

158
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:57,839
Yes.

159
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:31,839
Master Murong,

160
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,840
I held back eighty percent

161
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,600
of my power in that strike.

162
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:38,000
Your daughter's life
shouldn't be in danger.

163
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,759
Please don't hold this

164
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,159
against me.

165
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:43,879
Continue.

166
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:44,960
Yes.

167
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:53,080
Mr. Song has delivered
all three strikes.

168
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,600
Now, will everyone hear

169
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,919
what Peng Dasheng has to say?

170
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:02,480
Amitabha.

171
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:05,200
Mr. Peng,

172
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,559
say whatever you have to say.

173
00:09:06,559 --> 00:09:09,480
We'll make sure justice is done.

174
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,200
Thank you, Master.

175
00:09:16,039 --> 00:09:17,120
I have a question for Mr. Song.

176
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,679
Recently, countless sects

177
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:21,399
have been slaughtered by the Demon Sect.

178
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,600
So why has the Yizihuijian Sect

179
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:25,159
always been spared?

180
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,519
Mr. Song, do you have

181
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:28,120
some special charm

182
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:31,120
that makes the Demon Sect
steer clear of you?

183
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,919
What does that prove?

184
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,399
I run my sect well.

185
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:39,440
The Demon Sect
simply doesn't dare provoke us.

186
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:41,440
Fine.

187
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,639
Then answer this.

188
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,000
Over the past year,

189
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:47,480
whenever a smaller sect

190
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,840
was wiped out by the Demon Sect,

191
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:51,639
why were you always the first to arrive?

192
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:52,480
You took in their surviving disciples

193
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,440
and turned their sects
into your own branches.

194
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,720
Through that alone,

195
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,639
you gained hundreds of branches

196
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,240
and thousands of disciples.

197
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:02,000
Are you telling me
that was all a coincidence?

198
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,799
You...

199
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:08,679
That's nothing
but your side of the story.

200
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,799
Everyone,

201
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:13,840
he's accusing me of colluding
with the Demon Sect

202
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:17,080
based on nothing
but rumors and speculation.

203
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:20,000
Does anyone here find that convincing?

204
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,720
That does seem questionable.

205
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,240
That's true.

206
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,639
That makes sense.

207
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:25,200
It's not enough to prove anything.

208
00:10:25,919 --> 00:10:27,720
Amitabha.

209
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:32,120
Mr. Peng, do you have any other evidence

210
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:34,799
to support your claim?

211
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:37,200
Master, the evidence is almost here.

212
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,320
Nonsense!

213
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:42,679
You're obviously stalling for time.

214
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,120
Everyone,

215
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:46,840
is today's Martial Arts Assembly

216
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:50,279
being held for Peng Dasheng alone?

217
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:54,879
Mr. Peng, if you can't produce
more evidence right now,

218
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:56,840
perhaps we should revisit this

219
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:59,799
another day.

220
00:10:59,879 --> 00:11:00,720
What do you think?

221
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,879
The evidence is here.

222
00:11:25,759 --> 00:11:26,799
Honored elders,

223
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,200
this man is the proof you asked for.

224
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,360
I was a disciple
of the Yizihuijian Sect.

225
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:35,559
A few days ago,

226
00:11:35,559 --> 00:11:36,799
I saw Mr. Song

227
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:38,120
meeting with members of the Demon Sect.

228
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,360
Afraid he would kill me to silence me,

229
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,799
I fled Gusu that very night

230
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,799
and sought refuge in Jiangbei.

231
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,600
As long as you do as you're told,

232
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:52,240
you can have all
the Five Minerals Powder you want.

233
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:55,200
I won't fail you,

234
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,440
even if it costs me my life.

235
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:05,519
One of Nongxiao Pavilion's scouts
recently learned

236
00:12:05,519 --> 00:12:07,799
that a disciple of the Yizihuijian Sect
had fled to Jiangbei.

237
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,240
The scout reported it to me,

238
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,720
so I brought him back to Gusu overnight

239
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,600
to testify against

240
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,559
Song Qingbo in person.

241
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,000
Song Qingbo,

242
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:23,360
the evidence against you is undeniable.

243
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:25,480
What do you have to say?

244
00:12:32,399 --> 00:12:33,679
You scoundrel!

245
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,240
If it weren't for you,

246
00:12:36,799 --> 00:12:39,600
I'd already be commander
of the allied forces!

247
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:42,679
Why are you so determined
to ruin my plans?

248
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:46,279
You put Lin Dun up to it,
and Xiaojiu died because of you.

249
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:48,039
Today,

250
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:51,480
you'll pay for her death
with your own blood.

251
00:12:52,159 --> 00:12:53,080
Is that so?

252
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:54,679
Fine.

253
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:59,440
Then let's see
whether you have what it takes.

254
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:31,000
The Yizihuijian Sect's
Zhougong Sword Art

255
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,720
truly is the finest sword art
under heaven.

256
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,519
His Thousand-Sword Control

257
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:36,720
is truly extraordinary.

258
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,919
Mr. Peng is fending off thousands
of swords with only a broadsword.

259
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,679
He won't last long.

260
00:13:40,879 --> 00:13:41,759
That's right.

261
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,120
You little brat.

262
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,200
I really underestimated you.

263
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:02,360
I never thought
even my Zhougong Sword Art

264
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,440
would fail to defeat you.

265
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,240
Zhougong Sword Art, my foot.

266
00:14:05,799 --> 00:14:07,759
You're the shameless one here.

267
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,480
You've got a smart mouth.

268
00:14:09,879 --> 00:14:11,559
Since you're so eager to die,

269
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:13,360
I'll grant your wish.

270
00:14:25,879 --> 00:14:27,519
The Qi-Condensed Sword!

271
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,020
♪Come on♪

272
00:14:42,540 --> 00:14:44,220
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

273
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:49,140
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

274
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:52,340
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

275
00:14:52,580 --> 00:14:55,420
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

276
00:14:55,820 --> 00:14:58,420
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

277
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:01,900
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

278
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:05,140
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

279
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:08,220
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

280
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:11,140
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

281
00:15:11,700 --> 00:15:15,020
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

282
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:18,060
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

283
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:23,740
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

284
00:15:24,140 --> 00:15:26,180
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

285
00:15:26,740 --> 00:15:29,260
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

286
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:32,380
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

287
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:36,180
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

288
00:15:36,780 --> 00:15:38,900
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

289
00:15:39,820 --> 00:15:41,940
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

290
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:45,380
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

291
00:15:45,420 --> 00:15:49,700
♪I am my own king♪

292
00:16:02,780 --> 00:16:04,340
♪I emerge into the world♪

293
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:06,100
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

294
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:07,460
♪My pride is my trump card♪

295
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:09,260
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

296
00:16:09,260 --> 00:16:10,660
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

297
00:16:10,660 --> 00:16:12,420
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

298
00:16:12,420 --> 00:16:13,940
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

299
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:15,660
♪I dare to break every rule♪

300
00:16:15,660 --> 00:16:16,980
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

301
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:18,820
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

302
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:20,060
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

303
00:16:20,060 --> 00:16:22,300
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

304
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:23,820
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

305
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:25,420
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

306
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:27,020
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

307
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:28,740
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

308
00:16:28,740 --> 00:16:30,460
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

309
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:31,820
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

310
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:33,460
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

311
00:16:33,460 --> 00:16:34,940
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

312
00:16:34,940 --> 00:16:36,660
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

313
00:16:36,660 --> 00:16:38,260
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

314
00:16:38,260 --> 00:16:39,820
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

315
00:16:39,820 --> 00:16:44,140
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

316
00:16:44,140 --> 00:16:46,300
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

317
00:16:46,300 --> 00:16:48,900
♪Let me write the legend♪

318
00:16:53,780 --> 00:16:56,340
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

319
00:16:56,340 --> 00:16:59,660
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

320
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:02,140
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

321
00:17:02,140 --> 00:17:06,220
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

322
00:17:06,580 --> 00:17:09,180
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

323
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:11,660
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

324
00:17:11,660 --> 00:17:14,700
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

325
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:19,740
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
